Yeah.

418
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:20,000
E dema sûqî dikutan çî digotin? Mêro.
 
What did they say when they crushed with the sûqî? Men.

419
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:23,000
Lo mêra kilam digotin. Mêheylet wê dadan, çend cûrek aval
