There was no mill.

442
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,000
Ev gundê Xaledî min in.
 
This village of my maternal uncles.

443
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:44,000
Ez xwarzî yê vê gundî me.
 
I am the nephew of this village.

444
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,000
