No... before that it was Çeqelme.

467
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,000
Berî we Çeqelme ye.
 
Before that it was Çeqelme.

468
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:12,000
Berê we Çeqelme ye, yeko gotî, navî xwe Mihemed bî, ne Hesen
