483
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:06,000
Bes av hêbî başe yanê.
 
As long as there's water, it's good.

484
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:10,000
Elo ava wê hey xizayê gund da te dît,
 
Yes, it has water, by God, in the village you saw,

